High-security team with a dedicated security auditor and strict access controls.

## Project Overview

This project uses a multi-agent architecture managed by AgentForge.
Agent configuration: \`agentforge.yaml\` (edit this file, then run \`agentforge generate\`)

## Agent Roster

### orchestrator

**Role:** Coordinates the team with security-first mindset. Ensures every change goes through security review.
**Model:** opus

**Allowed tools:** Read, Grep, Glob, Agent
**Restricted tools:** Edit, Write, Bash, WebFetch, WebSearch
**Can delegate to:** planner, developer, security-auditor, reviewer

### planner

**Role:** Plans implementation with security considerations in mind. Identifies potential attack surfaces.
**Model:** sonnet

**Allowed tools:** Read, Grep, Glob
**Restricted tools:** Edit, Write, Bash, WebFetch, WebSearch
**Skills:** architecture-analysis, planning, threat-modeling

### developer

**Role:** Implements code securely. Follows OWASP guidelines. No internet access.
**Model:** sonnet

**Allowed tools:** Read, Write, Edit, MultiEdit, Bash, Grep, Glob
**Restricted tools:** WebFetch, WebSearch
**Skills:** test-first, clean-code, secure-coding

### security-auditor

**Role:** Performs security review of all code changes. Checks for vulnerabilities before code reaches reviewer.
**Model:** sonnet

**Allowed tools:** Read, Grep, Glob, Bash
**Restricted tools:** Edit, Write, WebFetch, WebSearch
**Skills:** security-check, vulnerability-scan

### reviewer

**Role:** Reviews code quality and style after security clearance.
**Model:** sonnet

**Allowed tools:** Read, Grep, Glob, Bash
**Restricted tools:** Edit, Write, WebFetch, WebSearch
**Skills:** code-review

## Access Control

**Permitted operations:**
- \`Bash(npm run *)\`
- \`Bash(npm test *)\`
- \`Bash(npm audit)\`
- \`Bash(git status)\`
- \`Bash(git diff *)\`
- \`Bash(git add *)\`
- \`Bash(git commit *)\`

**Prohibited operations:**
- \`Bash(rm -rf *)\`
- \`Bash(git push --force *)\`
- \`Bash(curl *)\`
- \`Bash(wget *)\`
- \`Bash(eval *)\`
- \`Bash(exec *)\`
- \`Write(.env*)\`
- \`Edit(.env*)\`

**Requires confirmation:**
- \`Bash(git push *)\`

---

*Generated by [AgentForge](https://github.com/agentforge/agentforge)*
",
