**Permitted operations:**
- \`Bash(npm run *)\`
- \`Bash(npm test *)\`
- \`Bash(git status)\`
- \`Bash(git diff *)\`
- \`Bash(git add *)\`
- \`Bash(git commit *)\`
- \`Bash(npx *)\`

**Prohibited operations:**
- \`Bash(rm -rf *)\`
- \`Bash(git push --force *)\`
- \`Write(.env*)\`
- \`Edit(.env*)\`

**Requires confirmation:**
- \`Bash(git push *)\`

