Single enhanced developer agent with safe defaults for individual developers.

## Agent Team

This project uses a multi-agent setup. Delegate tasks to the appropriate agent:

| Agent | When to use |
|-------|-------------|
| **developer** | Full-stack developer agent. Reads, writes, edits files and runs commands. Use for any development task. |

## Security Boundaries

- Sandbox is **enabled**
- Blocked operations: Bash(rm -rf *), Bash(git push --force *), Write(.env*), Edit(.env*)
- Allowed shell commands: Bash(npm run *), Bash(npm test *), Bash(git status), Bash(git diff *), Bash(git add *), Bash(git commit *), Bash(npx *)

